| File | Mechanism | Noise | Notes |
|---|---|---|---|
| `laplace_mechanism.py` | Noisy count/sum | Laplace | Basic ε-DP mechanism. |
| `gaussian_mechanism.py` | Noisy count/sum | Gaussian | (ε,δ)-DP and zCDP. |
